EN - US

## How to Run

1. Install Python 3
2. Install Pygame:


pip install pygame


3. Run the project:


python eos.py


## Controls

* Move the mouse over Eos to interact with it.
* Click on the screen to make Eos move toward that location.
* Click and drag objects to interact with the environment.
* Feed Eos using the "Dar comida" button.
* Try clicking on Eos repeatedly and see what happens...
